		<b>Comment By robert greene, 3-20-08</b>
		<p>what are the ususal suspects?<br />
are they different for bookstores<br />
or are they different for stores in boulder?</p>
		
		<b>Comment By Jenny Shank, 3-20-08</b>
		<p>Hi Robert,<br />
<br />
I intended the "usual suspects" to mean the reasons Nye cited for closing--such as competition from Barnes & Noble and Amazon.  Those are the entities that independent booksellers seem to often point to when they have trouble staying afloat.  The one thing she blames that is specific to Boulder is limited parking near her store.</p>
		
